										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Choosing a good trading broker is not as simple as it may seem; you need to carry out thorough research to ensure your safety and security. You’ll have to look into laws and regulations just as much as you look into transparency, costs, and how quickly the platforms can execute transactions. On top of that, you must determine what your goals and expectations are over both the short and the long term, as this is what will inform your strategy and the ways in which you navigate the market.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The broker you work with needs to match these specific requirements, provide you with the types of assets and products you want to invest in, allow you to create an account that is tailored to your needs, and support you with strong customer service throughout the way. If you’ve already started doing your research into which option would be best for you, then you’ve most likely already come across </span><a href="https://www.xs.com/en/" data-wpel-link="exclude"><span style="font-weight: 400;">XS forex broker</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, one of the most popular trading brokers in the world.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">What is XS?</span></h2>
