<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">XS.com is a multi-asset online broker that was first established in Australia in 2010. Since then, it has evolved into a global fintech company with offices all around the world. It specializes in a wide range of trading services and instruments, including forex, metals, energy, indices, shares, commodities, and cryptocurrencies, allowing you to build a robust portfolio and generate higher returns. Both retail and institutional investors work with </span><a href="https://www.xs.com/en/" data-wpel-link="exclude"><span style="font-weight: 400;">XS CFD broker</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, as the platform operates with both MetaTrader 4 and 5 as their tools.</span></p>
