<h2><b>What Trading Markets Are AI Trading Bot Apps Suitable For?</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">AI trading bot apps are used across different financial markets, but each market has different risks, trading hours, liquidity, and automation needs. For mobile users, the best AI trading bot app depends on whether they want to automate crypto trading, stock trading, forex trading, ETF investing, or multi-asset portfolio management.</span></p>
