<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Crypto trading is one of the most common areas for AI trading bot apps because the market runs 24/7. Unlike stocks, Bitcoin, Ethereum, and other digital assets can move sharply at night, on weekends, and during global news events.</span></p>
