<h3><b>5. Multi-Asset Trading</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Some AI trading bot platforms support more than one market, such as crypto, stocks, forex, indices, or commodities. These tools are suitable for users who do not want to rely on only one asset class.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Multi-asset AI trading apps can help users compare opportunities across different markets and manage broader trading strategies from one place.</span></p>
