<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Good for users who want trading and automation in one platform</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Easier than custom algorithmic trading</span></li>
